    ###
    ###  Neahttadigisánit maintainer tasks
    ###
    
    Svn up relevant configuration files and translation files
    
        $ fab local update_configs

    Updating dictionaries & FSTs
    
        $ fab local PROJECT compile
    
    Updating just the lexicon
    
        $ fab local PROJECT compile_dictionary
    
    Updating translation strings
    
        $ fab local update_strings
    
    Testing configuration (run before restart, always)

        $ fab local PROJECT test_configuration
    
    Restarting services
    
        $ fab local PROJECT restart_service
    
    Find a language
    
        $ fab local where_is:ISO

